data.description: Welcome Home to this delightful home near Brashear Lake in Levelland. Including three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, with a galley kitchen that includes tremendous storage. The backyard has an inviting covered patio, a 16x20 workshop, storage shed and above ground pool with a custom deck. Contact your favorite Realtor to schedule a showing!
